import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client';
import './index.css';
import App from './App';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom';



ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
     
  <Router>
    <Routes>
      <Route path="/Login" index element={<Login/>}/>
      <Route path="/Login/Dashboard" element={<Dashboard/>}/>
      <Route path="/" element={<Login/>}/>
      <Route path="/Dashboard"  element={<Dashboard/>}/>
      <Route path="/Serveur"  element={<Serveur/>}/>
      <Route path="/Client"  element={<Client/>}/>
      <Route path="/ViewClient/:id"  element={<ViewClient/>}/>
      <Route path="/Client/AddClient"  element={<AddClient/>}/>
      <Route path="/ViewServer"  element={<ViewServeur/>}/>
      <Route path="/VVM"  element={<VVM/>}/>
      <Route path="/Settings"  element={<Settings/>}/>
      <Route path="/LoadingDashboard"  element={<LoadingDashboard/>}/>
      <Route path="*" element={<Page404/>}/>
    </Routes>
  </Router>
</React.StrictMode>,
document.getElementById('root')
);
